{"ID":"20240726132744-e50r8vy","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240726132744-e50r8vy","title":"IAP","type":"doc","updated":"20250719135026"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240819111035-z3td9q4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240819111035-z3td9q4","updated":"20240819112153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"IAP流程"}]},{"ID":"20240819112105-r4pvyk4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240819112105-r4pvyk4","updated":"20240819112153"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"APP程序生成步骤（生成.bin文件）"}]},{"ID":"20240819111036-ps82gr1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240819111036-ps82gr1","updated":"20240819111058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.设置APP程序起始地址和存储空间大小的要求"}]},{"ID":"20240819111101-xwbt5fr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240819111101-xwbt5fr","updated":"20240819111129"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"strong text","TextMarkTextContent":"设置APP起始地址注意点"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"}]},{"ID":"20240819105910-sx37i3e","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240819105910-sx37i3e","updated":"20240819105911"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240819105913-g0bkzed","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240819105913-g0bkzed","updated":"20240819105913"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240819105913-5krbuc0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240819105913-5krbuc0","updated":"20240819105944"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"APP要在BootLoader后面"}]}]},{"ID":"20240819105944-vvme7hd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20240819105944-vvme7hd","updated":"20240819105944"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240819105944-pdd187m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240819105944-pdd187m","updated":"20240819105950"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"内存不能出现重叠"}]}]},{"ID":"20240819105951-60ow8wc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20240819105951-60ow8wc","updated":"20240819105951"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240819105951-up2yxgs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240819105951-up2yxgs","updated":"20240819110018"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"偏移量是0x200的倍数"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240819110021-7e0d3zt","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240819110021-7e0d3zt","updated":"20240819111439"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.设置中断向量偏移量"}]},{"ID":"20240819111440-96763ls","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240819111440-96763ls","updated":"20240819111723"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240819111453-m5ea6s7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240819111453-m5ea6s7","updated":"20240819111453"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240819111453-k9ikd3k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240819111453-k9ikd3k","updated":"20240819111657"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"APP存放在FLASH仲得设置方法        SCB-\u003eVTOR = FLASH_BASE | 0x10000;"}]}]},{"ID":"20240819111657-1n78jqr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20240819111657-1n78jqr","updated":"20240819111723"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240819111657-qq89hfk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240819111657-qq89hfk","updated":"20240819111723"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"APP存放在SRAM仲得设置方法        SCB-\u003eVTOR = SRAM_BASE | 0x1000;"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240819111739-1onhrcm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240819111739-1onhrcm","updated":"20250113163140"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.设置MDK编译后运行fromelf.exe，生成.bin文件"}]},{"ID":"20240924154022-22szlt4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240924154022-22szlt4","updated":"20250719135002"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"flash地址怎么设置"}]},{"ID":"20250113163141-p14ot61","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20250113163141-p14ot61","updated":"20250113163207"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#define FLASH_APP1_INFO_ADDR_START (0x1C00)\n#define FLASH_APP1_INFO_ADDR_END   (0x1FFF)\n\n0x1C00 到 0x1FFF 覆盖 1024 个字节，刚好是 1KB。\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20250113163208-45revnj","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20250113163208-45revnj","updated":"20250113163229"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250113163219-u70y1ul","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-u70y1ul","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在计算地址范围时，加 1 是因为地址范围包括了起始地址和结束地址，即它是**一个闭区间**，例如 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"[起始地址, 结束地址]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-cnu4y33","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-cnu4y33","updated":"20250113163219"}},{"ID":"20250113163219-uzsgw7d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-uzsgw7d","updated":"20250113163227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解释：闭区间 vs 开区间"}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-noyvi2w","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-noyvi2w","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250113163219-en4jml0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-en4jml0","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250113163219-njefrjm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-njefrjm","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果不加 1，计算的是**两地址之间的差值**，即 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"[起始地址, 结束地址)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 的范围（左闭右开区间，不包含结束地址）。"}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-909deau","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-909deau","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250113163219-o7603xu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-o7603xu","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250113163219-w4kmdn4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-w4kmdn4","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"但在实际中，地址范围通常是**闭区间**，既包含起始地址，也包含结束地址。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-jo94upe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-jo94upe","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250113163219-we3sovx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-we3sovx","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加 1 是为了包括结束地址。例如："}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-zb9dq2s","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-zb9dq2s","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250113163219-dni0v59","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-dni0v59","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250113163219-z01ep5w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-z01ep5w","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"0x1C00"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 到 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"0x1FFF"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 的字节数，实际是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"0x1C00"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"0x1C01"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"0x1C02"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ ... 到 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"0x1FFF"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，共有 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"(0x1FFF - 0x1C00 + 1)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 个地址。"}]}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-46fsxpq","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-46fsxpq","updated":"20250113163219"}},{"ID":"20250113163219-lpan7ef","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-lpan7ef","updated":"20250113163225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"例子：从 1 到 10"}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-ahklqys","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-ahklqys","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"假设你数从 1 到 10 有多少个数："}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-ywamrum","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-ywamrum","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250113163219-p90je8f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-p90je8f","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250113163219-uc7fl3g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-uc7fl3g","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"直接减法："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"10 - 1 = 9"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​（不包含 1 和 10 的所有中间数的差值）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-l8hbhsa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-l8hbhsa","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250113163219-5fzrs31","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-5fzrs31","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实际上：你要包括 10，所以结果是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"10 - 1 + 1 = 10"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-jnedtmt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-jnedtmt","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同样地，内存地址也是这样处理的。"}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-0ckfj4g","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-0ckfj4g","updated":"20250113163219"}},{"ID":"20250113163219-rosq4wy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-rosq4wy","updated":"20250113163229"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"公式"}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-pk3yefd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-pk3yefd","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"地址范围的计算公式是："}]},{"ID":"20250113163219-wcrnl1x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250113163219-wcrnl1x","updated":"20250113163219"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\text{总大小} = (\\text{结束地址} - \\text{起始地址}) + 1"}]}]},{"ID":"20250120102438-a9kh2dc","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20250120102438-a9kh2dc","updated":"20250120102440"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n * Copyright (C) 2017-2019 Alibaba Group Holding Limited\n */\n\n/*\n * .text(code)\tCode segment, the area where the program execution code is stored \n * .rodata(ro)\tRead-only data segment, storing strings in C and define constants\n * .data(rw) \tInitialize the data segment, store the initialized global variables and static variables in the program \n * .bss(zi)    \tUninitialized and initialized to 0 data segment, storing uninitialized(initialized to 0) global variables and static variables in the program;\n * .heap\t\tStores the dynamically allocated memory segment during the running of the process \n * .stack\t\tStore local variables temporarily created by the program \n *\n *  RO SIZE \t= (Code + RO Data) = (text + rodata)\n *  RW SIZE \t= (Rw Data + ZI Data) = (data + bss)\n *  ROM SIZE \t= (Code + RO Data + RW Data)\n */\n/******************************************************************************\n * @file     gcc_csky.ld\n * @brief    csky linker file\n * @version  V1.0\n * @date     09. June 2021\n ******************************************************************************/\nMEMORY\n{\n\tROM(RX)   : ORIGIN = 0x00000000,  LENGTH = 128K\n\tRAM(RWX)  : ORIGIN = 0x20000000,  LENGTH = 32K\n}\n\n/*heap and stack*/\n__heap_size  = 0x00;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t/* heap for dynamically allocated memory */\n__stack_top = ORIGIN(RAM) + LENGTH(RAM);\n__stack_start = __stack_top - 8 - __heap_size; \n\n/*PROVIDE (__ram_end  = 0x00008000); */\t\t\t/* define symbol for external reference*/\n/*PROVIDE (__heap_end = __ram_end);  */\n\nREGION_ALIAS(\"REGION_TEXT\",    ROM);\t\t\t/* Assign alias names to memory regions */\nREGION_ALIAS(\"REGION_RODATA\",  ROM);\nREGION_ALIAS(\"REGION_DATA\",    RAM);\nREGION_ALIAS(\"REGION_BSS\",     RAM);\n\nENTRY(Reset_Handler)\t\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Entrance address */\n\nSECTIONS {\n    .text :\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n    {\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Align the start of the section */\n        *crt0.o (.text)\t\t\t\t\t\t/* The file linked to the start position is startup.o */\n\t\t. = 0x108;\n\t\t*crt0.o(.vectors_inrom*)\n        *(.text)\n\t\t*(.text.*)\n    } \u003e REGION_TEXT\n\n    .rodata :\n    {\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\n        *(.rodata) \n        *(.rodata.*)\n\t\t*(.srodata) \n        *(.srodata.*)\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ; \n        _end_rodata = . ;\n    } \u003e REGION_RODATA\n\n    .data : \n    { \n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Align the start of the section */\n\t\t_start_data = .;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Provide the name for the start of this section */\n\t\t*crt0.o(.vectors_inram*)\n\t\tKEEP(*csp.o(.data.*))\t\t\t\t/* keep keyword to prevent it from being optimized */\n\t\tKEEP(*csp.o(.data))   \n    \t*( .data );\n\t\t*( .data.* );\n\t\t*( .sdata );\n\t\t*( .sdata.* );\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Align the start of the section */\n    \t_end_data = .; \t\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Provide the name for the end of this section */\n    } \u003e REGION_DATA AT \u003e REGION_RODATA\t\t\n   \n   .bss :\n    {\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\n\t\t_bss_start = . ;\n\t\t*(.sbss)\n\t\t*(.sbss.*)\n\t\t*(.scommon)\n\t\t*(.bss)\n\t\t*(.bss.*)\n\t\t*(COMMON)\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\n\t\t_ebss = . ;\n\t\t_end = . ;\n\t\t/* end = . ; */\n    } \u003e REGION_BSS AT \u003e REGION_BSS\n\n\t._user_heap_stack (DEFINED(__stack_start) ? __stack_start : .) (NOLOAD) : \t\t\t\n\t{\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\t\t\t\t\n\t\t*(.stack*)\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t/* stack region\t*/\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\n\t\t_end_stack = . ;\n\t\t__heap_start = . ;\n\t\t. += __heap_size ;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* heap region for dynamically allocated memory */\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\n\t} \u003e REGION_BSS AT \u003e REGION_BSS\n}\n\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20250120102506-padwyeb","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20250120102506-padwyeb","updated":"20250120102507"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n * Copyright (C) 2017-2019 Alibaba Group Holding Limited\n */\n\n/*\n * .text(code)\tCode segment, the area where the program execution code is stored \n * .rodata(ro)\tRead-only data segment, storing strings in C and define constants\n * .data(rw) \tInitialize the data segment, store the initialized global variables and static variables in the program \n * .bss(zi)    \tUninitialized and initialized to 0 data segment, storing uninitialized(initialized to 0) global variables and static variables in the program;\n * .heap\t\tStores the dynamically allocated memory segment during the running of the process \n * .stack\t\tStore local variables temporarily created by the program \n *\n *  RO SIZE \t= (Code + RO Data) = (text + rodata)\n *  RW SIZE \t= (Rw Data + ZI Data) = (data + bss)\n *  ROM SIZE \t= (Code + RO Data + RW Data)\n */\n/******************************************************************************\n * @file     gcc_csky.ld\n * @brief    csky linker file\n * @version  V1.0\n * @date     09. June 2021\n ******************************************************************************/\nMEMORY\n{\n\tROM(RX)   : ORIGIN = 0x00004000,  LENGTH = 112K\n\tRAM(RWX)  : ORIGIN = 0x20000000,  LENGTH = 32K\n}\n\n/*heap and stack*/\n__heap_size  = 0x00;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t/* heap for dynamically allocated memory */\n__stack_top = ORIGIN(RAM) + LENGTH(RAM);\n__stack_start = __stack_top - 8 - __heap_size; \n\n/*PROVIDE (__ram_end  = 0x00008000); */\t\t\t/* define symbol for external reference*/\n/*PROVIDE (__heap_end = __ram_end);  */\n\nREGION_ALIAS(\"REGION_TEXT\",    ROM);\t\t\t/* Assign alias names to memory regions */\nREGION_ALIAS(\"REGION_RODATA\",  ROM);\nREGION_ALIAS(\"REGION_DATA\",    RAM);\nREGION_ALIAS(\"REGION_BSS\",     RAM);\n\nENTRY(Reset_Handler)\t\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Entrance address */\n\nSECTIONS {\n    .text :\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n    {\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Align the start of the section */\n        *crt0.o (.text)\t\t\t\t\t\t/* The file linked to the start position is startup.o */\n\t\t. = 0x108;\n\t\t*crt0.o(.vectors_inrom*)\n        *(.text)\n\t\t*(.text.*)\n    } \u003e REGION_TEXT\n\n    .rodata :\n    {\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\n        *(.rodata) \n        *(.rodata.*)\n\t\t*(.srodata) \n        *(.srodata.*)\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ; \n        _end_rodata = . ;\n    } \u003e REGION_RODATA\n\n    .data : \n    { \n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Align the start of the section */\n\t\t_start_data = .;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Provide the name for the start of this section */\n\t\t*crt0.o(.vectors_inram*)\n\t\tKEEP(*csp.o(.data.*))\t\t\t\t/* keep keyword to prevent it from being optimized */\n\t\tKEEP(*csp.o(.data))   \n    \t*( .data );\n\t\t*( .data.* );\n\t\t*( .sdata );\n\t\t*( .sdata.* );\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Align the start of the section */\n    \t_end_data = .; \t\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Provide the name for the end of this section */\n    } \u003e REGION_DATA AT \u003e REGION_RODATA\t\t\n   \n   .bss :\n    {\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\n\t\t_bss_start = . ;\n\t\t*(.sbss)\n\t\t*(.sbss.*)\n\t\t*(.scommon)\n\t\t*(.bss)\n\t\t*(.bss.*)\n\t\t*(COMMON)\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\n\t\t_ebss = . ;\n\t\t_end = . ;\n\t\t/* end = . ; */\n    } \u003e REGION_BSS AT \u003e REGION_BSS\n\n\t._user_heap_stack (DEFINED(__stack_start) ? __stack_start : .) (NOLOAD) : \t\t\t\n\t{\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\t\t\t\t\n\t\t*(.stack*)\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t/* stack region\t*/\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\n\t\t_end_stack = . ;\n\t\t__heap_start = . ;\n\t\t. += __heap_size ;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* heap region for dynamically allocated memory */\n\t\t. = ALIGN(0x4) ;\n\t} \u003e REGION_BSS AT \u003e REGION_BSS\n}\n\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20250719134951-n0lcyxa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250719134951-n0lcyxa","updated":"20250719134951"}},{"ID":"20250719134954-danvvdh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20250719134954-danvvdh","updated":"20250719135026"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数据传输方式"}]},{"ID":"20250719135005-cfadi3m","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20250719135005-cfadi3m","updated":"20250719135026"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250719135011-r05dr2u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250719135011-r05dr2u","updated":"20250719135026"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"uart+DMA+空闲"}]}]}]}